   <conbody>
      <div class="- topic/div ">
         <hazardstatement type="caution" class="+ topic/note hazard-d/hazardstatement ">
            <messagepanel class="+ topic/ul hazard-d/messagepanel ">
               <typeofhazard class="+ topic/li hazard-d/typeofhazard ">risk of crushing and Sharp edges</typeofhazard>
               <howtoavoid class="+ topic/li hazard-d/howtoavoid ">Always use protective gloves when unpacking the system.</howtoavoid>
            </messagepanel>
         </hazardstatement>
         <p class="- topic/p ">Use the right tool depending on
the construction of the crate/frame:<ul class="- topic/ul ">
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">For screws use a screwdriver.</p>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">For metal clamps use a flat screwdriver.</p>
               </li>
            </ul>
            <note class="- topic/note ">For solid crates it is not necessary to remove the skids.</note>
         </p>
         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Remove the top with the correct tool.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p ">Remove the side walls with the correct tool one after another
until all side walls are removed.</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
         <p class="- topic/p ">Now the system is on the pallet with the inner packing protection.</p>
